         <abstract id="aspace_bfe68fa1f71bed3ab48013991c6540a5">Yale University celebrated its 275th anniversary on 15 October 1976. The records primarily consist of background materials, drafts and transcripts of ceremonial remarks, and writings by invited speakers, including a commemorative poem by Archibald Macleish.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_de5c1fcddf3706aabbc9dcd88a7ff09a">
